  <title>Area</title>

  <introduction>

      
    <p>
       Area is the space covered or enclosed within the boundaries of a shape. 
    </p>
    <p>
      We calculate the area of different shapes such 
      as triangles, rectangles, squares, circles, and many others. 
    </p>

